Photos: WTC Transportation Hub’s mall gets its grand opening
The highly anticipated Westfield mall within the World Trade Center's Oculus is finally open
        Aug 16, 2016,  4:15pm EDT
Photos: WTC Transportation Hub’s mall gets its grand opening
Curbed Flickr Pool/Stefano Ravalli
The Westfield mall within the 
World Trade Center Oculus
 officially opened on Tuesday, drawing in crowds to shop the many new stores that have moved in as well as to rejoice in the grand opening ceremonies. Several performances were underway by local talent groups, the 
 musical performers, and Leslie Odom Jr., from 
, who all took to the stage. Eataly, Sephora, Aldo, Cole Haan, Kiehl’s, and Apple are just some of the many stores that opened their doors at their new home within Westfield.
Naturally, attendees shared photos and videos of the event on social, offering a sense of excitement and energy present for the new mall that has been 15 years in the making.
Grand opening of the Westfield World Trade Center mall happening today. The mall is located in the Santiago Calatrava designed oculus which opened in March. #wtc #westfieldwtc #wtcoculus #wtctransportationhub #lowermanhattan #nyc #newyork #architecture #retail #infrastructure #calatrava #curbed #nycprimeshot #streetdreamsmag #icapture_nyc #ig_nycity #nycbuildings #newdevelopment #newyorkcity #iphone
